## What is this?

The ORDEM PrintAgent is a Windows service that connects your restaurant's thermal printers to the ORDEM system. It runs in the background and handles kitchen tickets and fiscal invoice printing automatically.

## Installation

1. Download `Ordem.PrintAgent.exe` from the [latest release](../../releases/latest)
2. Run it as Administrator
3. Paste the pairing code generated from the ORDEM web panel (Settings → Print Agent)
4. The agent installs itself as a Windows service — no manual configuration needed

